    public abstract class HstoreCountTypeHandler<KEY extends Comparable>
extends org.apache.ibatis.type.BaseTypeHandler<Map<KEY,Integer>>
    A mybatis type handler that translates from the typed java.util.Map to the postgres hstore database type. Any non integer values in hstore are silently ignored. As we do not map all java map types to this mybatis handler apply the handler manually for the relevant hstore fields in the mapper xml, for example see DatasetMetricsMapper.xml.
